<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 00:36:50 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列右翼声称受到迫害。这是无耻的谎言</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israels-right-wing-claims-to-be-persecuted-its-a-shameless-lie/00000191-2d8c-d200-a9f9-adcd6e7a0000</link><description>对某些人不平等地运用法律，同时又未能追究其他人的责任的做法在以色列可以追溯到很久以前，但不是针对右翼</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 20:18:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israels-right-wing-claims-to-be-persecuted-its-a-shameless-lie/00000191-2d8c-d200-a9f9-adcd6e7a0000</guid></item><item><title>美国：“比以往任何时候都更接近”加沙停火；西方外交官称谈判仍陷入僵局</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/u-s-closer-than-ever-to-cease-fire-in-gaza-western-diplomats-say-talks-still-stuck/00000191-2e0e-d4e9-a7b7-2fce7d1c0000</link><description>国家安全委员会发言人约翰·柯比声称协议已经摆在桌面上，但参与以色列与哈马斯谈判的西方外交官否认了解谈判取得突破</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 19:45:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/u-s-closer-than-ever-to-cease-fire-in-gaza-western-diplomats-say-talks-still-stuck/00000191-2e0e-d4e9-a7b7-2fce7d1c0000</guid></item><item><title>在以色列最后的常态堡垒中，紧张地等待伊朗的报复</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-07/ty-article/.highlight/in-israels-last-bastions-of-normalcy-waiting-nervously-for-irans-revenge/00000191-2d53-d1b4-a399-7df7cc470000</link><description>这种等待的游戏是攻击的一部分——哈桑·纳斯鲁拉甚至说过同样的话——也许伊朗和真主党希望悬念确实会杀死我们</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 18:48:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-07/ty-article/.highlight/in-israels-last-bastions-of-normalcy-waiting-nervously-for-irans-revenge/00000191-2d53-d1b4-a399-7df7cc470000</guid></item><item><title>美国犹太人在观看以色列的犹太至上主义暴徒时并没有感到更安全</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-08-07/ty-article-opinion/.premium/u-s-jews-dont-feel-safer-when-they-watch-israels-jewish-supremacist-mobs/00000191-2806-dbbc-ab95-3957c76c0000</link><description>如果以色列想继续成为所有犹太人的家园，就不能放松对保护所有人的民主自由价值观的警惕</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 17:33:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-08-07/ty-article-opinion/.premium/u-s-jews-dont-feel-safer-when-they-watch-israels-jewish-supremacist-mobs/00000191-2806-dbbc-ab95-3957c76c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战事第 306 天：世卫组织将向加沙运送超过 100 万支脊髓灰质炎疫苗</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-306-who-to-send-gaza-over-one-million-polio-vaccines/00000191-2dbe-da6f-af99-2dfe6cee0001</link><description>白宫表示，“我们距离达成我们所认为的最接近”的人质释放/停火协议 ■ 据报道，联黎部队官员的家属已从黎巴嫩撤离 ■ 土耳其正式要求加入南非对国际法院的诉讼，指控以色列在叙利亚实施种族灭绝加沙 ■ 德国和法国拒绝接受以色列财政部长的言论，即让 200 万加沙人挨饿是“正确且道德的” ■ 战争已过去 306 天，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 17:00:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-306-who-to-send-gaza-over-one-million-polio-vaccines/00000191-2dbe-da6f-af99-2dfe6cee0001</guid></item><item><title>以色列新闻频道忠实内塔尼亚胡首席执行官因记者强烈反对而被撤换</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/newly-appointed-ceo-of-israeli-new-channel-to-be-replaced-after-journalists-backlash/00000191-2d8e-d1b4-a399-7dae6d8f0000</link><description>尤利娅·沙马洛夫-贝尔科维奇被任命为以色列第 13 频道的负责人是有争议的，因为她公开支持内塔尼亚胡的立场，但在她被记录说“电视台里有很多坏记者”后，员工的反抗导致该频道宣布她将被任命为以色列第 13 频道的负责人。被取代</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 16:47:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/newly-appointed-ceo-of-israeli-new-channel-to-be-replaced-after-journalists-backlash/00000191-2d8e-d1b4-a399-7dae6d8f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列部长与 Black Cube 就监视亲巴勒斯坦的美国学生团体举行会谈</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-minister-held-talks-with-black-cube-about-spying-on-pro-palestinian-u-s-students/00000191-2d2b-d927-a5b5-ff7f03690000</link><description>侨民事务部长 Amichai Chikli 于 6 月与 Black Cube 会面，讨论可能对巴勒斯坦学生正义组织执行间谍任务，该组织在美国校园领导反以色列抗议活动。该部称 Black Cube 向其提出了这个想法，但消息人士称事实恰恰相反</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 15:19:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-minister-held-talks-with-black-cube-about-spying-on-pro-palestinian-u-s-students/00000191-2d2b-d927-a5b5-ff7f03690000</guid></item><item><title>法国和德国猛烈抨击以色列斯莫特里奇关于饿死加沙人的言论</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/france-germany-slam-israels-smotrich-for-comments-on-starving-gazans-to-death/00000191-2d2f-d4ad-a7ff-fd3fc82b0000</link><description>法国和德国外交部谴责这位右翼部长，几天前他暗示国际压力是以色列不让加沙人饿死的唯一原因</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 15:15:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/france-germany-slam-israels-smotrich-for-comments-on-starving-gazans-to-death/00000191-2d2f-d4ad-a7ff-fd3fc82b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列周围的火圈：伊朗、真主党和胡塞武装的军火库</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/the-ring-of-fire-around-israel-a-look-at-the-arsenals-of-iran-hezbollah-and-the-houthis/00000191-2ce3-d927-a5b5-ffff7b5c0000</link><description>从远程巡航导弹到携带炸弹的无人机，以色列的敌人可能会对其防空系统进行前所未有的考验</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 14:29:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/the-ring-of-fire-around-israel-a-look-at-the-arsenals-of-iran-hezbollah-and-the-houthis/00000191-2ce3-d927-a5b5-ffff7b5c0000</guid></item><item><title>超过 110 名记者在加沙被杀。以色列同行保持沉默</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opi