法国、德国、意大利和英国也发函表达了对以色列被排除在外的共同担忧</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 10:55:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/u-s-ambassador-to-japan-to-skip-a-bomb-memorial-service-because-israel-was-not-invited/00000191-2c62-d7d8-a7bb-ee7a3c1a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方突击搜查外交部，怀疑在发放外交护照方面存在不法行为——包括向内塔尼亚胡的儿子发放外交护照</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/police-raid-foreign-ministry-on-suspicion-of-illegally-granting-diplomatic-passports/00000191-2c19-d32b-ad9f-3d3b58c50000</link><description>据两名官员称，正在调查的其中一本护照是给总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡的儿子亚伊尔·内塔尼亚胡的护照</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 09:20:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/police-raid-foreign-ministry-on-suspicion-of-illegally-granting-diplomatic-passports/00000191-2c19-d32b-ad9f-3d3b58c50000</guid></item><item><title>海法居民担心真主党的罢工将针对该市的危险材料港口区</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/haifa-residents-fear-hezbollah-strike-will-target-citys-hazardous-materials-port-area/00000191-2bc2-d1b4-a399-7fe6b2ce0000</link><description>在真主党领导人纳斯鲁拉提到海法是火箭袭击的潜在目标后，尽管以色列军队下令减少石化产品库存，但其居民仍担心会发生危险材料事件</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 08:59:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/haifa-residents-fear-hezbollah-strike-will-target-citys-hazardous-materials-port-area/00000191-2bc2-d1b4-a399-7fe6b2ce0000</guid></item><item><title>AIPAC 的另一场胜利：韦斯利·贝尔 (Wesley Bell) 和 850 万美元击败“小队”成员科里·布什 (Cori Bush)</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/another-victory-for-aipac-wesley-bell-and-8-5-million-defeat-squad-member-cori-bush/00000191-2adb-d2a9-a5dd-3edb30180001</link><description>亲以色列游说团体的联合民主项目称赞这一结果“进一步证明亲以色列是两党的好政策和好政治”</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 03:29:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/another-victory-for-aipac-wesley-bell-and-8-5-million-defeat-squad-member-cori-bush/00000191-2adb-d2a9-a5dd-3edb30180001</guid></item><item><title>西方大国越来越担心俄罗斯与伊朗的合作不断发展</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/western-powers-increasingly-concerned-about-growing-russia-iran-cooperation/00000191-2911-d642-a9d5-bb51462b0000</link><description>在有报道称俄罗斯正在向伊朗提供军事援助并试图向胡塞武装提供武器后，西方外交官发出了警报。一位外交官告诉《国土报》，“俄罗斯的介入让我们非常担心，以色列也应该担心”</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 03:01:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/western-powers-increasingly-concerned-about-growing-russia-iran-cooperation/00000191-2911-d642-a9d5-bb51462b0000</guid></item><item><title>对于真主党来说，以色列痛苦的等待是其报复的一部分，但它仍然希望避免战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/for-hezbollah-israels-agonizing-wait-is-part-of-its-revenge/00000191-2950-d642-a9d5-bb50d8a50000</link><description>哈桑·纳斯鲁拉周二在贝鲁特发表了激烈的演讲，但没有明确威胁爆发地区战争——他的组织及其伊朗赞助人显然仍在寻求避免这种情况</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 03:00:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/for-hezbollah-israels-agonizing-wait-is-part-of-its-revenge/00000191-2950-d642-a9d5-bb50d8a50000</guid></item><item><title>白宫：比以往任何时候都更接近停火协议，美国将帮助保卫以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article-live/nasrallah-nerve-racking-anticipation-part-of-hezbollah-response-goal-to-exhaust-israel/00000191-2a95-dcd6-abf7-7e975efc0000</link><description>报告：伊朗建议民用航空公司避免在周四上午 4:00 至 7:00 之间飞越其领空 ■ 伊朗外长表示，其回应将“在正确的时间以适当的形式”做出 ■ 白宫：我们正在比以往任何时候都更接近达成停火协议 ■ 土耳其正式要求加入联合国法院针对以色列的种族灭绝案 ■ 戈兰地区委员会：以色列北部居民必须留在避难所附近，并尽量减少不必要的旅行</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 02:12:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article-live/nasrallah-nerve-racking-anticipation-part-of-hezbollah-response-goal-to-exhaust-israel/00000191-2a95-dcd6-abf7-7e975efc0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列总检察长告诉内塔尼亚胡：你的内阁工作程序有缺陷，损害公共利益</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/israels-ag-tells-netanyahu-your-cabinets-work-procedures-are-flawed-harm-the-public/00000191-293d-d1b4-a399-7dbf1ec20000</link><description>加利·巴哈拉夫-米亚拉（Gali Baharav-Miara）在给总理的信中表示，内阁秘书发布的法律意见超越了他的职权，“在安全领域产生了严重影响”</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 22:17:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/israels-ag-tells-netanyahu-your-cabinets-work-procedures-are-flawed-harm-the-public/00000191-293d-d1b4-a399-7dbf1ec20000</guid></item></channel></rss>